-- Barclays Hires Sha Luo From CRU as Cross-Commodities Analyst
-- B y   M a r i a   K o l e s n i k o v a
-- 2012-08-30T09:35:36Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-30/barclays-hires-sha-luo-from-cru-as-cross-commodities-analyst.html
Barclays Plc said it hired Sha Luo
from CRU Strategies as a London-based cross-commodities analyst
with an additional focus on commodity investing and quantitative
analysis.  Luo started last week and works on the research team, led
by London-based Paul Horsnell, spokeswoman Aurelie Leonard said
in an e-mail today. Luo joined Barclays from CRU, where she was
a cross-commodities consultant.  The bank said yesterday it hired Sijin Cheng as a
commodities analyst in  Singapore . Cheng started working on
